类 NutritionService.NutritionData

java.lang.Object
service.NutritionService.NutritionData
封闭类:
NutritionService
public static class NutritionService.NutritionData extends Object
Inner class representing nutritional data for an ingredient. Contains calorie, protein, fat, and carbohydrate information per 100 grams.
从以下版本开始:
1.0
